metadata.title: Sleeping Child Unformat
metadata.sourceFile: Michael Learns To Rock - Sleeping Child Unformat.ttml

lines.text: The Milky Way upon the heavens
And Mr. Moon, he came by
Gonna show them all we care
But you've built your own paradise
If all the people around the world
They had a mind like yours
We'd have no fighting and no wars
There would be lasting peace on Earth
If all the kings and all the leaders
Could see you here this way
They would hold the Earth in their arms
They would learn to watch you play
But you've built your own paradise
I'm gonna cover my sleeping child
Keep you away from the world so wild
Keep you away from the world
Away from the world so wild
But you've built your own paradise
But you've built your own paradise
